      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single load configuration (ASTM F1717 standard geometry, 10° offset, room temperature). Only one test condition was evaluated; the required level of 3 demands multiple conditions spanning the COU space. This factor does not meet the required level and represents a known gap in the validation evidence. Accepted under risk-informed rationale: model influence is Medium and the single condition is the most clinically relevant."
